[thinking] **Considering MethodHandles and coverage**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about how MethodHandles find things at runtime. It seems the coverage agent might exclude those reflective calls when counting dynamic access. It recognizes that Class.forName is called, but I'm curious if it captures direct "reachability metadata" instrumentation. This whole subject is a bit complex, and I want to make sure I'm getting the details right.
